column5: Got out a little late today 4 till 6.hit a spot where i have yet to catch but had seen others do ok.Was determined to get one outta there,and the god,s where with me today.Took 2 on spinner and one on pink worm.what a beauty day wish i had got out earlier
nice shootin man ....i contemplated hitting the river at 4ish but decided to run the dogs instead....i do have tired dogs now but with the storm comming i think i made a mistake...  Good onya
Nice going. I've seen that rock somewhere(lol)
Great looking fish, I am jealous.
Nice fish...that looks like fun.....also very refreshing to see a steelhead report where the fish seems the focus of the pic and not what shiny new reel you have
